OL,3,CEngland legend Paul Gascoigne holds
OL,4,Cback tears as he discusses addiction
OL,6,FPaul Gascoigne tells Good Morning
OL,7,FBritain how he is the 'best he's felt
OL,8,Fin years' and shares a message of
OL,9,Fencouragement for the England squad
OL,10,Fahead of the 2026 World Cup
OL,12,FEngland legend Paul Gascoigne welled
OL,13,Fup with emotion as he revealed that
OL,14,Fpeople struggling with addiction have
OL,15,Ftold him his memoir had "saved their
OL,16,Flives".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
