OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781111161
OL,3,CEngland legend Paul Gascoigne holds
OL,4,Cback tears as he discusses addiction
OL,6,FThe former Midfielder, whose fame hit
OL,7,Fdizzying heights after his appearance
OL,8,Fat the Italia '90 World Cup, told Good
OL,9,FMorning Britain that after years
OL,10,Falcoholism, he is doing well and is
OL,11,Fthe "best he's felt in years".
OL,13,FAffectionately known as Gazza,
OL,14,FGascoigne is open about his addiction
OL,15,Fin his latest book, "Eight", which
OL,16,Funlike his previous autobiographies,
OL,17,Fhe says is "not about football".
OL,19,FHe teared up as he told GMB: "A lot of
OL,20,Fpeople have come up and said they've
OL,21,Fread it and how it's saved their life.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781111161
OL,3,CEngland legend Paul Gascoigne holds
OL,4,Cback tears as he discusses addiction
OL,6,F"If that book can save one person's
OL,7,Flife, then I've done my job, I think I
OL,8,Fshould read it myself you know."
OL,10,FNot only does he detail his struggles
OL,11,Fwith drinking, Gascoigne also writes
OL,12,Fabout a period of his life where he
OL,13,Fwas addicted to Red Bull, drinking 30
OL,14,Fcans of the energy drink per day at
OL,15,Fone point.
OL,17,FHe said ended up flying to Arizona to
OL,18,Fattend rehab for his Red Bull
OL,19,Faddiction, adding: "The withdrawal was
OL,20,Fhorrific."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@`O]
