OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781111161
OL,3,CEngland legend Paul Gascoigne holds
OL,4,Cback tears as he discusses addiction
OL,6,FAsked what he thought of England's
OL,7,Fchances at the 2026 World Cup, which
OL,8,Fkicks off this month, Gazza said: "I
OL,9,Fthink the first one is going to be a
OL,10,Ftough one, because Croatia are a good
OL,11,Fteam.
OL,13,F"We must get at least a draw and it
OL,14,Fgives them a chance in the second
OL,15,Fgame. You can't afford to carry
OL,16,Fanyone. Everyone's got to be on the
OL,17,Fball and the team spirit as well is
OL,18,Fimportant."
OL,26,@pD@cOUuD@AOUzD@KO]
