OL,3,CEngland legend Paul Gascoigne holds
OL,4,Cback tears as he discusses addiction
OL,6,FIn a message to the players, he said:
OL,7,F"Enjoy it because you never know, it
OL,8,Fcould be your last World Cup. The most
OL,9,Fimportant thing is team spirit,
OL,10,Fbecause that goes a long way."
